narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Research idea development, proposal structures and grant proposal writing skills.
I developed the most useful skill during this course, writing good grant proposals!

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Each student gets chance to work with Prof. Honeychurch individually. It is very helpful for each of us developing ideas and improving our work.
No weakness at all. It was well organised so that each student can develop skills potentially.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: It's a course that make one's research ideas upgrade.
Yes definitely. You should take this course for your future career!
